    {
      "text": "folder 90 - 146\nG-91\n\nIn Malebranche's terms, the representation in normal experience is by no means clear. It would be of accidents + fails in terms of the \"one mother three times, not three mothers\" abstraction - a cognitive insight derived, however, from perception. The flux is not stabilized by the organizational power of the constants (eide). It is a very limited perception. Mostly chaotic, mostly of epiphenomena + the transitory. Probably the missing factor is a cognitive leap of meta-abst",
      "matched_alias": "Dasein",
      "term_id": "TERM_dasein",
      "term_name": "Dasein",
      "term_slug": "dasein"
    }
  ],
